      "content": "it feels like people only want to help me keep living in this misery. but there isn't any relief coming. the doctors just give me more pills that don't work and tell me to \"cope.\" i'm not looking for a text line, i'm looking for an exit. is it really so wrong to think that wanting to end the suffering is actually the most logical, merciful thing for someone in my position?",
